  "Eliminating all non-essential expenses": "",
  "Grouping spending into defined categories like housing, food, transportation, and entertainment to identify patterns": "",
  "Ranking expenses from most to least expensive": "",
  "Expense categorization groups individual transactions into meaningful categories. This reveals where money actually goes versus where you think it goes, often uncovering surprising spending patterns.": "",
